{"id": "1411006455364194534", "channel_id": "1411006455364194534", "type": 0, "author_id": "705407952575529022", "author_name": "water_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "簡單來說\n莉莉天賦表示獲得的忍耐量提升\n莉莉超限表示獲得等同最大生命值的忍耐\n那麼莉莉超限獲得的忍耐是否會受到天賦的影響而變高呢\n目前是不會受到天賦影響\n但還是不確定這是不是對的", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T15:15:54.191000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1411006456484069517", "filename": "IMG_20250829_230951.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 35501, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411006455364194534/1411006456484069517/IMG_20250829_230951.jpg?ex=69ff4faa&is=69fdfe2a&hm=ebeda0c9be433c0f74860a0240bd982243fae750fe140940e98d708db5300db0&"}, {"id": "1411006457083859026", "filename": "IMG_20250829_230703.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 19746, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411006455364194534/1411006457083859026/IMG_20250829_230703.jpg?ex=69ff4faa&is=69fdfe2a&hm=e88b4c03be622d1073d1615144ac103dda558799984f645687b826f8e68ce89b&"}, {"id": "1411006457801080872", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2025-08-29-23-05-04-212.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 2029705, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411006455364194534/1411006457801080872/Screenrecorder-2025-08-29-23-05-04-212.mp4?ex=69ff4faa&is=69fdfe2a&hm=f0284ee6e6730a21cfeba9ba1ae44fa9225bd81b2494d3a11ca0cf682fc1b25d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411006455364194534", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」關於莉莉超限是否應該受到天賦影響的提問", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1410976789177696317", "channel_id": "1410976789177696317", "type": 0, "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "author_bot": false, "content": "As can be seen in the screenshots, the flame fx for the fiamma stack is not showing here. I used a bunch of Kathigura cards from ultra turn and the last one did not get the fiamma fx when it got affected by it", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T13:18:01.221000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1410976789488205944", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-08-29-20-08-57-970_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 211805, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1410976789177696317/1410976789488205944/Screenshot_2025-08-29-20-08-57-970_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69ff3409&is=69fde289&hm=aafc664019eac58e5fb9010dc90af7aa311a202c3fee1cfe3f6648d207f55afa&"}, {"id": "1410976790314225734", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-08-29-20-09-05-305_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 232775, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1410976789177696317/1410976790314225734/Screenshot_2025-08-29-20-09-05-305_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69ff3409&is=69fde289&hm=ef8b7e56da4047caeeea9004449b5acbfc1e1446b8194c23362055a723505113&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410976789177696317", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Kath Fiamma FX not showing", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1410995709305421854", "channel_id": "1410995709305421854", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "With the amount of entries that Archive has, it is very time consuming to click onto every single one of them, in order to get the „new“ message for the Archive icon in the main menu to leave. Having a „seen all“ or „read all“ button that just allows you to mark everything as seen (like we have in the „Notice“ menu (pic for reference)) would be helpful to finally have that „new“ message gone instead of for having to click on every single thing that is in the archives.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T14:33:12.131000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1410995709699817544", "filename": "IMG_6049.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 955941, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1410995709305421854/1410995709699817544/IMG_6049.png?ex=69ff45a8&is=69fdf428&hm=b489a7fe3cc27b43d261c271f66629b8445b49b878f154d02d58722386805623&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410995709305421854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Add „seen all“ button for Archive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1411083473481105448", "channel_id": "1411083473481105448", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "I copied Ericas \"Mechanical Barrier\" with Echoed Simulation and it didn't do anything, I got no additional stacks of Taunt nor of Fortress. \nI have not done any testing with other cards so I only know of this faulty interaction. If this interaction is intended as such, then Echoed Simulation should not be able to copy Mechanical Barrier and other cards that it shouldn't be able to interact with, and Echoed Simulation should explain what can and cannot be copied. But I suppose this is just a faulty interaction instead so i will report it as a bug.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T20:21:56.741000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-29T20:22:40.862000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411083473481105448", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」[PVP] Ramona's \"Echoed Simulation\" does not copy cards as expected", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1410922459385040937", "channel_id": "1410922459385040937", "type": 0, "author_id": "1403431686116741143", "author_name": "2300011747", "author_bot": false, "content": "剧情里面有提到过设定唤醒体主要有四个界域血肉、深海、混沌、超维。但是也提及了存在一些稀少的界域比如以太。想问一下游戏后续开发的时候会考虑到这个设定引入全新界域机制以及新界域的角色吗》", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T09:42:07.989000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410922459385040937", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于游戏后续内容的一点疑问", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801", "1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1410998403307143278", "channel_id": "1410998403307143278", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "When you go to the banners and select „Details“ at the bottom left, you are presented with the rules for the currently selected banner. However, the History shows the history for the banner that you last pulled on and not the currently selected banner. Sure, you can just use the drop down menu to change which banners history you are looking at, but having the shown history be the history of the currently selected banner by default would be a nice addition.", "timestamp": "2025-08-29T14:43:54.431000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1410998403307143278", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Make „Records“ show details for current banner by default", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
